      "id": "PopularPost91241",
      "post_content": "I rather like Blood Lust. Sure, Fists is a straight pump with no disadvantage, but it's easy to turn the /-4 into a benefit: put it on [Doran, the Siege Tower](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doran, the Siege Tower), suddenly he becomes a 1/1. Put it on one of those annoying new blue sphinxes and get them in [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt) range. And the drawback will never kill *your* creature by itself.  \n  \nSolid red utility spell.",
      "posted_by": "Ideatog",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost91241\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I rather like Blood Lust. Sure, Fists is a straight pump with no disadvantage, but it's easy to turn the /-4 into a benefit: put it on <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Doran, the Siege Tower\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doran, the Siege Tower\">Doran, the Siege Tower</a>, suddenly he becomes a 1/1. Put it on one of those annoying new blue sphinxes and get them in <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a> range. And the drawback will never kill <i>your</i> creature by itself.<br/><br/>Solid red utility spell.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '91241'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2063\">Ideatog</span>\r\n                                (7/26/2010 10:17:05 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\